ATTRIBUTION NOTICE:

This software is inspired by architectural patterns observed in FlexPBX,
a proprietary VoIP management system. No proprietary code from FlexPBX
has been copied or included in this implementation.

The following concepts were used as inspiration only:
- AMI connection management patterns
- Conference bridge control interfaces
- Dial plan rule structures
- Extension monitoring approaches

All code in this project is original implementation based on:
- Public Asterisk AMI documentation
- Standard VoIP best practices
- Model Context Protocol specifications
- Open source software design patterns
